{"jobType":"yuexin","section":"skill","subsection":"产妇护理","difficulty":"hard","type":"choice","question":"哺乳期抑郁 SSRI 首选？","options":[{"text":"舍曲林 L2 级","score":10},{"text":"氟西汀大剂","score":4},{"text":"帕罗西汀停药","score":3},{"text":"MAOI 抑制剂","score":0}],"explanation":"舍曲林乳汁分泌少（LactMed L2）首选；帕罗西汀次选；氟西汀半衰期长慎用大剂量。","source":"NIH LactMed 数据库"}
